snippet.title: Rahul Gandhi Says Modi's Demonetisation a War on the Poor to Benefit the Rich

localized.description:
Congress vice-president Rahul Gandhi alleges that Prime Minister Narendra Modi's cashless move has made the poor. Rahul Gandhi said that Modi's demonetisation a war on the poor to benefit the rich.
